    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new-to-you ride? I'm parting with this beauty and it's in really solid shape! It's been well-loved and runs like a champ, making it perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend getaways. I've made sure to keep up with the basics so it's ready to hit the road the moment you hop in. It\u2019s a fantastic, dependable car that still has so much life left in it. I\u2019d love for it to go to a great home, so come by and check it out\u2014I'm sure you'll fall in love with how it drives!",
