    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a pinnacle of analog performance, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal power delivery to the rear wheels. Critical maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement, ensuring structural and mechanical longevity. The chassis retains its signature 50/50 weight distribution with MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension, providing exceptional lateral stability. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals are robust and track-ready.",
