    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "This vehicle is a stellar example of pride in ownership, offering a reliable and polished driving experience. The exterior finish retains a brilliant luster, though a careful eye will note a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel\u2014typical signs of careful use that do not detract from its overall sharp appearance. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free. The leather upholstery is supple with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster, and all interior electronics, including the dual-zone climate control and infotainment system, operate flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a comprehensive log of records included. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil service and a brake pad replacement within the last 5,000 miles. On the road, it handles with precision, the engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts without hesitation. It comes complete with two sets of keys and the original owner's manuals, making it a turnkey option for a buyer seeking a well-documented, dependable vehicle.",
